{"query":"query persons($skip: Int, $take: Int) {
  persons(skip: $skip, take: $take) {
      # non citizenCard data
      id
      username
      email
      roles
      createdDate
      # extended non citizenCard data
      mobilePhone
      postal
      city
      region
      geoLocation
      timezone
      personalInfo
      internalInfo
      profile
      # citizenCard data    
      firstname
      lastname
      gender
      height
      fatherFirstname
      fatherLastname
      motherFirstname
      motherLastname
      birthDate
      nationality
      country
      documentNumber
      documentType
      cardVersion
      emissionDate
      expirationDate
      emittingEntity
      identityNumber
      fiscalNumber
      socialSecurityNumber
      beneficiaryNumber
      pan
      requestLocation
      otherInformation
      registrationDate
  }
}","variables":{"skip":0,"take":50},"operationName":"persons"}

{"query":"query personById($id: String!){
  personById(id: $id) {
      # non citizenCard data
      id
      username
      email
      attributes {
        id
        content
        issuedDate
        expiresDate
        expired
        certifierID
      }
      roles
      participant {
        id
        name
        msp
        identities {
          id
          status
          fingerprint
        }
      }
      identities {
        id
        status
        fingerprint
      }
      createdDate
      # extended non citizenCard data
      mobilePhone
      postal
      city
      region
      geoLocation
      timezone
      personalInfo
      internalInfo
      profile
      # citizenCard data    
      firstname
      lastname
      gender
      height
      fatherFirstname
      fatherLastname
      motherFirstname
      motherLastname
      birthDate
      nationality
      country
      documentNumber
      documentType
      cardVersion
      emissionDate
      expirationDate
      emittingEntity
      identityNumber
      fiscalNumber
      socialSecurityNumber
      beneficiaryNumber
      pan
      requestLocation
      otherInformation
      registrationDate
  }
}","variables":{"id":"{{ personId  }}"},"operationName":"personById"}

{"query":"mutation personAddAttribute($personId: String!, $addPersonAttributeData: AddPersonAttributeInput!) {
  personAddAttribute(personId: $personId, addPersonAttributeData: $addPersonAttributeData) {   
      # non citizenCard data
      id
      username
      email
      attributes {
        id
        content
        issuedDate
        expiresDate
        expired
        certifierID
      }
      roles
      participant {
        id
        name
        msp
        identities {
          id
          status
          fingerprint
        }
      }
      # extended non citizenCard data
      mobilePhone
      postal
      city
      region
      geoLocation
      timezone
      personalInfo
      internalInfo
      profile
      # citizenCard data    
      firstname
      lastname
      gender
      height
      fatherFirstname
      fatherLastname
      motherFirstname
      motherLastname
      birthDate
      nationality
      country
      documentNumber
      documentType
      cardVersion
      emissionDate
      expirationDate
      emittingEntity
      identityNumber
      fiscalNumber
      socialSecurityNumber
      beneficiaryNumber
      pan
      requestLocation
      otherInformation
      registrationDate    
  }
}
","variables":{"personId":"{{ personId  }}","addPersonAttributeData":{"id":"born-year","content":{"data":"1971","work":true},"issuedDate":1554239270,"certifierID":"{{ participantId  }}"}},"operationName":"personAddAttribute"}
{"query":"subscription personLogged{\n  personLogged\n}"}
